title: Optimize "lazily".
pid: 8232c86b-3daf-484a-af44-bd68e67fdc6b
body: |2-
  "Wait until the last minute."
  Don't worry too much about catching performance problems early.
  Just represent things in the most natural way.
  But pay attention when things start eating too much time or space
  (or, and this is kind of new with AI, energy).
